data.description: Nostalgic charm, manicured side yard, covered front porch, shimmering chandeliers welcome you to this 1900s timeless home. Swoon over the oversized wood baseboards, stately sprawling staircase, elegant chandeliers and medallions, built ins w/ vintage shutters, dining buffet, statement pocket door throughout the main living spaces. Intimate yet functional kitchen with stained glass window, island, walk in pantry. Head upstairs where you'll find 3 bedrooms. The primary features 2 spacious walk in closets. The smallest room leads out towards a welcoming sun porch. Enjoy tile floor, claw foot tub w/ shower enclosure & oversized closet perfect for a dreamy walk in shower. The garage is located off the alley on the side of the house. Come see this awe-inspiring find yourself before it's gone!
